#: ../../source/unit/dds.rst:2 3270b363dd74470fae81fa29d1926bf1
msgid "DDS Unit"
msgstr "DDS Unit"

#: ../../source/unit/dds.rst:6 1d234ba3a1c0406ca8b92cf709364c90
msgid ""
"DDS is a signal source Unit. It uses the AD9833 programmable waveform "
"generator + STM32F0 micro controller. Based on I2C communication "
"interface (addr:0x31) It can easily control the signal source to output "
"multiple waveforms (sine wave, triangle wave, square wave output, "
"sawtooth wave, signal output amplitude 0-0.6V) and adjust the frequency "
"and phase."
msgstr ""
"DDS 是一个信号源 Unit。它使用 AD9833 可编程波形发生器 + STM32F0 微控制器。基于 I2C "
"通信接口（addr:0x31），可轻松控制信号源输出多种波形（正弦波、三角波、方波输出、锯齿波，信号输出幅度 0-0.6V），并可调节频率和相位。"

